<DIV type=1>

<HEAD weight="bold" >
How to use Terra-Cortril Nystatin Cream
</HEAD>


<BLOCK>
Pierce the tube by reversing the cap and screwing down to break the seal on the tube.
</BLOCK>


<BLOCK>
Clean the affected skin area as thoroughly as possible.
</BLOCK>


<BLOCK>
Gently apply a small amount of cream to the affected area. This may be done two to four times a day. The cream may be applied on a sterile gauze if infection is present.
</BLOCK>

<DIV type=2>

<HEAD>
Do not stop using the cream too soon after seeing improvement
</HEAD>


<BLOCK>
Terra-Cortril Nystatin Cream is for external use only. Do not use it for eye infections.
</BLOCK>

