<DIV type=1>

<HEAD weight="bold" >
What if the cream is accidentally
</HEAD>


</DIV>
<DIV type=1>

<HEAD weight="bold" >
swallowed?
</HEAD>


<BLOCK>
Terra-Cortril Nystatin Cream is for external use only. If any cream is accidentally swallowed, tell your doctor immediately, or contact your nearest hospital casualty department.
</BLOCK>


